Package com.googlecode.aluminumproject.parsers.aluscript.instructions

Interface Summary
Instruction An instruction for the AluScript parser.
 

Class Summary
AbstractInstruction Abstract superclass of instructions.
ActionInstruction Creates an action element and adds it to the context.
ExpressionInstruction Creates an expression element and adds it to the context.
LibraryInstruction Adds one or more library URLs and their abbreviations to the context, so that they can be referenced by upcoming instructions at the same nesting level.
NewlineInstruction Adds a text element that contains a newline to the context.
TabInstruction Adds a text element that contains a tab character to the context.
TextInstruction Creates a text element and adds it to the context.
